115
00:10:30,110 --> 00:10:31,080
it's impossible.

116
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:32,440
Yes.

117
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:37,550
Unless it's paranormal power,
or else it's scientifically impossible.

118
00:10:37,550 --> 00:10:39,240
I see.

119
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:42,080
Thank you.

120
